	<text>
		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Charleston</placeName> <date>Novr 28<hi rend="sup">th</hi>. 1858</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Dear Sir.</p>
			<p rend="indent(2)"><persName>Miss Esther Davidson</persName> of your city who is<lb/> an applicant for Governess in my family has referred me<lb/> to you&#44; in a recent letter&#44; to testify as to her character &#38;<lb/> capacity&#44; and as the position she will occupy is one of<lb/> importance I trust that with your usual frankness &#38;<lb/> kindness you will give me full particulars touching<lb/> her character&#44; disposition&#44; &#38; capabilities.&#8212;</p>
				<p>As she will be the companion of my wife and the Instruc<lb/>tress&#44; of four of my children three girls and one boy<lb/> whose ages vary from 12 to 6 years it is highly<lb/> important that I should be made acquainted<lb/> with her antecedents&#8212;</p>
				<p>I am asking to procure the services of a Lady who<lb/> while she is capable of teaching the varied <add>&#63;</add><lb/> of an english education can also impart lessons<lb/> in French&#44; Music&#44; &#38; Painting&#44; at the same time<lb/> I desire one who will also be enabled to cultivate<lb/> the moral sense&#44;&#8212;and while she improves the<lb/> mind will also train the heart&#8212;</p>
				<p>In selecting such a person I should be governed<lb/> in a great measure by the credentials of friends<lb/> of the party &#38; if therefore your recommendation of<lb/> <persName>Miss Davidson</persName> embodies my views &#38; wishes I<lb/> will take great pleasure in securing her</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>services or that of any other person you may<lb/> be pleased to recommend.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">Anticipating an early and favourable<lb/> response.</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">I remain</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">Very respectfully</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)">Your obdt Servt</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">B. Mordecai</persName></p>
		</body>
